    Title: I Ching
Title: Getting Ahead
---
The time is propitious for the assertion of authority -- to inspect, comfort,
and rule. Great progress and success will be realized. But spring does not
last forever, and the favorable trend will reverse itself in due time. The
wise man foresees evil and handles its threat accordingly.
